item.title: Macros Without Bugs or Flowers III - Death
item.description: I submitted “Death” for the Macros Without Bugs or Flowers III challenge at DPChallenge. I came in 170 out of 196 with a score of 4.38 / 10. Granted, it’s not really a macro shot by the truest definition, but I did have a lot of fun reading the comments… WARNING IMAGE 4151221101 COULD NOT BE FOUND

item.title: Lighting IV - Darkened Lantern
item.description: I submitted “Darkened Lantern” for the Lighting IV challenge at DPChallenge. I came in 157 out of 190 with a score of 4.61 / 10. Personally, I like the shot, so it all works out in the end. WARNING IMAGE 3442173831 COULD NOT BE FOUND

item.title: End - Graffiti
item.description: I submitted “Graffiti” for the End challenge at DPChallenge. I cam in 94 out of 145 with a score of 4.74 / 10. I think I may have over done the contrast on the shot, but it still turned out to be pretty interesting. WARNING IMAGE 3251607843 COULD NOT BE FOUND

item.title: Silence II - Lonely Winter Night
item.description: I submitted “Lonely Winter Night” for the Silence II challenge at DPChallenge. I came in 110 out of 177 with a score of 4.96 / 10. So far this is my best result at DPChallenge. I think that I may have over done the softening on the shot, but I still think it was a cool effect. WARNING IMAGE 3232537411 COULD NOT BE FOUND

item.title: Lucky - Natural 20
item.description: I submitted “Natural 20” for the Lucky challenge at DPChallenge. I came in 66 out of 85 with a score of 4.41 / 10. In 20⁄20 hindsight, I probably should have submitted the other version of that shot. Oh well. WARNING IMAGE 3175155980 COULD NOT BE FOUND
